{
  "stem": "10768.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But at that time, Leo already said, ask for a furlough for two days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he came with a pickup to our hospital, which gave him a chance to wash up because where he was there also, you didn't-- sometimes he had, sometimes he didn't have running water.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This is when I found out about the entire Holocaust, on my trip to Lublin, on my trip to Przemysl, and when I came back this was December, Christmas time.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Three days-- three weeks later was the main offensive, offensiv, offensive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We crossed the bridge on the Vistula river into Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So let me tell you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our hospital was a huge hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But because we were so close to the Vistula River, they told us, apparently in collaboration with the Russians, they say take three trucks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On one truck, take a tent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Take the basic instrument.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Take some medication, Lysol, whatever alcohol, whatever is need to do primary, very primitive first, first aid.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one-- on one truck was a little kitchen with the one who was cooking and some basic-- a little bit barley, a little bit whatever.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By the way, in Russia, the food was very, very meager.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when we  came already to Kiwerce at that time, we had already some meat, pork meat, in boxes in tins, which was sent from United States.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We felt already an improvement and even medication.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "While previously our supply of medication was very meager, at that time, it was meager too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We couldn't take too much on the truck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we had some.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So January 17, 1945, in the middle of the night we crossed the Vistula River.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were three trucks from our hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
